    {
      "page_number": 1,
      "raw_text": "A. Beamer, superintendent of\nthe Northern Pacific railroad, in a\nCommunication to the city council,\nstates that his company is not in a\nposition to outline it's ultimate\nplans on grade separation in this\ncity at the present time and asks\nthe city fathers to be lenient and\nallow more time."
